{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Restrict lorries to the left lane on dual carriageways and motorways",
        "additional_details": "I believe that doing 60mph in the middle lane is dangerous because blocking the left-hand and middle lanes during slow and prolonged overtakes can be hazardous.",
        "background": "Ban lorries and other slow moving vehicles restricted to 60 miles an hour from the middle and right hand lanes on motorways, and the right hand lane of a dual carriageway. They must be compelled to remain in the left lane regardless of traffic.",
